# Coding Agent Tools - Development Tools Reference

## Main Cheat-sheet

| Tool | Purpose | Key Flags |
|------|---------|-----------|  
| **`search`** | **Search files and content** | **`--files`, `--preset`** |
| `agent-lint` | Lint agent files | `--fix` |
| `capture-it` | Capture ideas/notes | `--type` |
| `code-lint` | Lint code files | `--fix` |
| `code-review` | Code review | `--preset` |
| `context` | Load context presets | `--preset` |
| `coverage-analyze` | Coverage analysis | `--format` |
| `create-path` | Create files/dirs | `--force` |
| `git-add` | Enhanced git add | `--patch` |
| `git-commit` | Enhanced git commit | `--intention` |
| `git-status` | Enhanced git status | `--verbose` |
| `git-tag` | Enhanced git tag | `--annotate` |
| `handbook` | Handbook access | `sync-templates` |
| `llm-query` | LLM query interface | `--model` |
| `nav-path` | Path navigation | `file` |
| `nav-tree` | Project tree | `--context` |
| `mcp-proxy` | MCP server proxy | `--port` |
| `release-manager` | Release management | `current` |
| `task-manager` | Task management | `--filter` |

**💡 Tip**: Use `search` for all searching and `nav-path file <filename>` instead of `find`.

